::Skulletron::

	Bloodystrike said that the defence system doesn't like weapon fire, so
Skulletron took his hand away from his gun.  Skulletron thought about where
to go next.  Then suddenly, for a moment, the word Torture was ringing in
his head.

	"No!  No!" Then the ringing stopped, "No! Uh, no place is more important
than the torture chamber!  You know, capturing all those Maximals and
Predacons!  They need to be tortured to even get a word out of 'em!"

	Skulletron had wondered why Torture had come to his head.  Could it have
anything to do with his past?  Oh well, no time to worry about that.  If he
was tormented in the past, he would get revenge by joining the Alliance and
serving Zardus.
